content: there’s a cheap dunk to be made here about the *aesthetics* of sterile, clinical bureaucracy, but i wanna try to avoid that. a lot of modernity has been about the glorious benefits of stainless steel, sanitation, antibiotics, even hard-fought basics like washing your damn hands
